<p><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; font-size: medium;"><strong><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong><strong><span style="color: #888888;"><strong><strong><span><strong><strong><span><a href="https://www.awangarda.olsztyn.pl/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2313&amp;Itemid=3527">"Ojczyzna" </a>- prod. Polska, Francja : godz. 20.00 <span style="color: #ffcc00;">sala arte</span></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></p>
